{
  "stem": "4226.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh that was probably-- couldn't give an exact date.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was on the-- must have been beginning of June",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] '44 June.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went-- we came to Dachau, not to the concentration camp, to the railway station, which is a small German station with three, four platforms.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And 500 of us were cut off, disembark from there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And 1,000 off to concentration camp in New Dachau.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were wait-- a German, there was an SS officer, a lieutenant, in whole uniform, leather jacket, leather long coat, and motorbike.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember a 250cc BMW in German military colors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and he had been a few guards there, and he had a short speech that I understand German a bit from what I learned in school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he said, you're going to work in this place, and you'll be well fed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We already-- we thought we would be fed before killed, like--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Like the fellows in the jungle, then eat us!",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Feed you before killing you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then we went off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "From there, the guards, 500, to-- we walked through nicely wheat fields.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The wheat was still on the field, getting yellow slightly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all this good smell of-- of wild flowers in the wheat field.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We came to a camp about an hour's walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no houses in the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nothing.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that camp, as we approached, we saw that it got no electric fences.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just ordinary wire fence, which-- what they use?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How you call that wire?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Barbed.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Barbed wire.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Thanks.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And four towers, it was a small camp with four guard towers on the four-- thing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And on a gate also from barbed wired wooden gate.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came in the camp, and we had to discard the clothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
